&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unlock Health is seeking an experienced and dynamic Associate Account Supervisor with a proven track record in health care communications/marketing. As an Associate Account Supervisor, you will play a pivotal role in leading strategic communications engagements by fostering client relationships, crafting effective omnichannel campaigns, and helping clients protect and promote the reputation of their organization through internal and external communications . This role will also support the growth of our healthcare portfolio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
