&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead day-to-day management of client account. Coordinate between client stakeholders and align internal teams across the agency, ensuring deadlines for project scopes and deliverables are met and any potential barriers are proactively identified and addressed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate on-going accountability by creating and managing project management materials, including status tracking documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support vendor management related to database development, consumer research, and call center services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help identify opportunities to expand scope of work with existing clients as part of business development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for key client stakeholders, and coordinate with the internal team to ensure effective support and successful delivery of client engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to meetings and update clients on all activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communications Development: &lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create comprehensive communication plans leveraging owned, earned, shared and paid media.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elevate and protect our clients reputation by building tactical strategies that effectively position their value in the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build narratives and engagement plans that increase trust, credibility and grow support among key audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strategic, targeted messaging, and materials to execute on approved strategies that enhances client reputation externally and aligns their organization internally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to creative concepting and asset development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write message platforms, initial drafts of all communications, creative briefs and prepare deliverables for final review with account lead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
