&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on industry trends, regulatory changes, and developments within the healthcare industry and managed care space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate insights into actionable recommendations for clients to stay ahead of the curve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn how to pivot campaigns based on negotiation progress and help clients scenario plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
