&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We&#39;re looking for a visionary technology leader to head our Web Development practice, someone who can bridge the gap between ambitious digital strategy and flawless execution. In this role, you&#39;ll own the technical direction of our web platforms, lead a talented cross-functional team, and directly shape the digital experiences of the enterprise clients we serve.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a senior leadership position that reports to the VP, Digital Experience. You&#39;ll work alongside C-suite stakeholders, practice leads, and client teams, serving as the authoritative technical voice in a fast-moving, innovation-driven environment. If you thrive at the intersection of technology, strategy, and people leadership, and you bring an AI-native mindset to everything you build, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
