&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with CX, UX/UI, content, creative, and strategy teams to deliver seamless, high-quality digital experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee multiple concurrent enterprise-scale projects, ensuring on-time, on-budget delivery without sacrificing quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex business and marketing requirements into practical, scalable technical solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set the Standard&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and enforce coding standards, security protocols, and compliance practices across all web platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
