&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a senior media leader who knows how to turn complexity into clarity, strategy into momentum, and integrated media into measurable business impact. You bring deep expertise across the full media ecosystem, including digital, social, programmatic, search, video/CTV, audio, traditional, OOH/DOOH, and emerging channels. More importantly, you understand how those channels work together to shape behavior, influence decision-making, and drive outcomes for healthcare clients.&lt;/p&gt;
