&lt;li&gt;Review and approve all major media recommendations before they are presented to clients, serving as the final media quality check to ensure strategic alignment, accuracy, and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide teams in developing holistic channel strategies across digital, social, programmatic, search, video/CTV, audio, traditional, OOH/DOOH, and emerging platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
