&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unlock Health is hiring a UX/UI Design Lead who combines exceptional craft with systems thinking, business acumen, and a passion for mentoring others. You are a design leader who thrives at the intersection of user needs, organizational goals, and technical feasibility — elevating both the work and the people around you.&lt;/p&gt;
