&lt;li&gt;Champion accessibility and inclusive design standards, ensuring all experiences meet usability and accessibility expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with strategists, developers, content teams, and stakeholders to ensure seamless implementation and alignment across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate client conversations, workshops, presentations, and stakeholder reviews with confidence and clarity.&lt;/li&gt;
